{"tha-ap383:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap383:0.2":"Avataphalavagga ","tha-ap383:0.3":"1 Avataphaladayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap383:1.1":"“Sataramsi nama bhagava, ","tha-ap383:1.2":"sayambhu aparajito; ","tha-ap383:1.3":"Vivekakamo sambuddho, ","tha-ap383:1.4":"gocarayabhinikkhami. ","tha-ap383:2.1":"Phalahattho aham disva, ","tha-ap383:2.2":"upagacchim narasabham; ","tha-ap383:2.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap383:2.4":"avatam adadim phalam. ","tha-ap383:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap383:3.2":"yam phalamadadim aham; ","tha-ap383:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap383:3.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap383:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap383:4.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap383:4.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap383:4.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap383:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap383:5.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","tha-ap383:5.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap383:5.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap383:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap383:6.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap383:6.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap383:6.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap383:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma avataphaladayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap383:8.1":"Avataphaladayakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}